You're not going to be unhappy.

567
00:59:21,024 --> 00:59:25,017
Are you unhappy?

568
00:59:25,261 --> 00:59:27,530
I love you.

569
00:59:27,530 --> 00:59:31,523
Fuck you!

570
00:59:32,969 --> 00:59:36,962
