728
01:25:14,309 --> 01:25:16,611
Are you buying?

729
01:25:16,611 --> 01:25:18,179
No, it's OK.

730
01:25:18,179 --> 01:25:22,172
You're mad, you've got two stations.

731
01:25:27,255 --> 01:25:31,248
OK, Marcel?

732
01:25:39,400 --> 01:25:41,870
